{
  "stem": "7337.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I took bookkeeping as well, but when the result-- when the exam was written, I couldn't balance the balance sheet, so I knew that I'd failed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a friend of mine said to me, you know, your name is up on the board.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The principal wants to see you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to see him at the technical college opposite the station, and he says, why don't you come and collect your bookkeeping certificate?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, well, how could I have passed?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I know that my balance sheet didn't pass-- didn't-- it didn't balance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, well, he'll make inquiries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he'd phoned me, and he said, please come and see me again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, look, your balance sheet was actually quite correctly put-- set out, but you took 20 schillings to the pound-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and 12-- no. 20-- 12 schillings to the pound, and 20 pence to the schilling.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's why it didn't balance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I became a qualified bookkeeper, [LAUGHS] despite the mistake.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my first job I found at Norman Anstey's, which was a department store, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] where I took-- where I became a window dresser, took a three-year course.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
